name: Bubblebones’ Humble Abode
description:
Dear friends,

Have you been well? Please don’t get burned out and have enough rests. Eat some yummy apple pies and clam chowders for better snuggles and sleeps. I’ve been packing up some extra feet muscles since living with Bubblebones. We’ve been skipping together to get to work, get groceries, and other shenanigans. Sometimes if I get too tired, Percy the Nessie lets me ride on his back. He’s Bubblebones’ trusty pet. I want one for my own, but housing nowdays don’t accomodate pets that are 25 feet long. bummer.

Gonna skip some more now to get swole. Housing options are still very much welcome if you have some. Until then, don’t litter and don’t forget to get some fresh air! hop hoppity hop

Love,
Jetson Humble
